<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. سَوْدَاءُ مُظْلِمَةٌ شَعْثَاءُ مُوحِشَةٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>دَهْمَاءُ مُحْرِقَةٌ لَوَّاحَةُ الْبَشَرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فِيهَا الْجَحِيمُ مُذِيبٌ لِلْوُجُوهِ مَعَ الْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَمْعَاءِ مِنْ شِدَّةِ الأحْرَاقِ وَالشَّرَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِيهَا الْغِسَاقُ الشَّدِيدُ الْبَرْدِ يَقْطَعُهُمْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِذَا اسْتَغَاثُوا بِحَرِّ ثُمَّ مُسْتَعِرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِيهَا السَّلاسِلُ وَالأَغْلالُ تَجْمَعُهُمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَعَ الشَّيَاطِينِ قَسْرًا جَمْعَ مُنْقَهِرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فِيهَا الْعَقَارِبُ وَالْحَيَّاتُ قَدْ جُعِلَتْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>جُلُودُهُمْ كَالْبِغَالِ الدُّهْمِ وَالْحُمُرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالْجُوعُ وَالْعَطَشُ الْمُضْنِي لأَنْفُسِهِمْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فِيهَا وَلا جَلَدٌ فِيهَا لِمُصْطَبِرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَهَا إِذَا مَا غَلَتْ فَوْرٌ يُقَلِّبُهُمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَا بَيْنَ مُرْتَفِع مِنْهَا وَمُنْحَدِرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>جَمْعُ النَّوَاصِي مَعَ الأَقْدَامِ صَيَّرَهُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كَالْقُوسِ مَحْنِيَّةً مِنْ شِدَّةِ الْوَتَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لَهُمْ طَعَامٌ مِن الزَّقُّومِ يَعْلَقُ فِي<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>حُلُوقِهِمْ شَوْكُهُ كَالصَّابِ وَالصَّبِرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يَا وَيْلَهُمْ تُحْرِقُ النِّيرَانُ أَعْظُمَهُمْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِالْمَوْتِ شَهْوَتُهُمْ مِنْ شِدَّةِ الضَّجَرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>